{
  "stem": "8784.5",
  "chunk_idx": 6,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "Of course, after a number of days, housing was assigned to us in a short while.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "Polish government assigned to us a former student building for housing of those people that were arriving.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And I lived in the student building in Krakow.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "We did not know what we will do with our lives from here on, but, again, the situation developed that the Poles were drafting people into the army.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And I realized that being the age of 20 at that time-- close to 20.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "I was 19-- that I was subject to draft.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "Now, I did a little quick thinking and realized that if I made myself one year younger, since I had no documents on me-- I have absolutely no documents.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "Nobody knows where I was born-- if I made myself one year younger and established this in some kind of a document, I might escape the army temporarily until I leave the country.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "And sure enough, that worked.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I was never drafted into the army.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And-- and I began living in Krakow for a short while.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "I developed a skill of being able to cross the borders illegally.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "And I went to Czechoslovakia with the attempt to bring some goods from Czechoslovakia to Poland, so I would sell this and make some money, so I would be able to support myself, because immediately after the war, there was no organization functioning that would help you, dish out even food.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "There was no Polish agency.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "There was no UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "There was no-- there were no Jewish organizations functioning that quickly after the war to really guide us, help us, or anything.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "After a number of days, there were Jewish organizations that began to function.",
      "word_count": 13
    }
  ],
